Server: aa04f096-2df9-487f-827b-32be316c7805
QueryId: wg85128:7070
QueryEngine: CUBE[name=viw_bikyn_achis_trans_day_v3]
SQL: select viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy as viw_bikyn_dim_date_yy
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_date_yy_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl.buss_chnl as viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl_buss_chnl
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl.buss_chnl_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl_buss_chnl_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media.trans_media as viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media_trans_media
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media.trans_media_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media_trans_media_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl.user_intnl_ins_id_cd as viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl_user_intnl_ins_id_cd
		,viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl.user_intnl_ins_cn_nm as viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl_user_intnl_ins_cn_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method.pay_method as viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method_pay_method
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method.pay_method_desc as viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method_pay_method_desc
		,sum(m.total_trans_num)*1.00 as total_trans_num
		,sum(m.settle_num)*1.00 as settle_num
from viw_bikyn_achis_trans_day m
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_date as viw_bikyn_dim_date on m.hp_settle_dt = viw_bikyn_dim_date.dt
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl as viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl on m.buss_chnl = viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl.buss_chnl
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media as viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media on m.trans_media = viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media.trans_media
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl as viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl on m.user_branch_cd = viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl.user_intnl_ins_id_cd
left outer join viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method as viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method on m.pay_method = viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method.pay_method
where 1=1   
group by viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy
		,viw_bikyn_dim_date.yy_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl.buss_chnl
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_buss_chnl.buss_chnl_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media.trans_media
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_trans_media.trans_media_desc
		,viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl.user_intnl_ins_id_cd
		,viw_bikyn_dim_ins_user_intnl.user_intnl_ins_cn_nm
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method.pay_method
		,viw_bikyn_dim_code_pay_method.pay_method_desc
